snippet.title: Official Gameplay Trailer - My Pet Rock
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam NOW!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1904400/My_Pet_Rock/

Planned Released: April 2022

My Pet Rock is a collection of mini games inspired by early arcade games and modern endless runners. If you are looking for a fun, aesthetically pleasing and relatively casual game to play then My Pet Rock is for you. Come and customize your newest pet, while earning the highest scores around.

Powered By: Unreal Engine 4

Developed By: Neon Wizard Games
Published By: Neon Wizard Games

Music In Trailer Video: All Out Attack by Makai Symphony | https://soundcloud.com/makai-symphony
Music promoted by https://www.chosic.com/free-music/all/
